\newlabel{tab:reward-mitigation}{{6}{9}{Reward-hacking mitigation from v3 to v5, computed from stored generations with the current reward implementation. Deg.\% is the fraction flagged by \texttt {\_is\_degenerate()}; $R_{\text {acc}}=0$\% is the fraction receiving zero content reward; Mean $R_{\text {acc}}$ is the average content reward. The comparison is a package-level ablation and does not isolate any single change.\relax }{table.caption.15}{}}
